                           </placeName>
                        </persName>, her right in a tenement in the <placeName key="place_107082">parish of Holy Trinity, W<supplied>allingford</supplied>
                        </placeName>, between the garden of <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>Louches</surname>
                        </persName> and the tenements of <persName>
                           <forename>Eustace</forename> the <pb n="152"/> 
                           <surname>goldsmith</surname>
                        </persName> and the said Thomas, in <placeName type="street" key="place_107014">Corteyslane</placeName>. 
                            Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>Nicholas</forename> de la <surname>Barre</surname>, mayor</persName>, 
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Swayn</forename> of <surname>Mortele</surname>
                        </persName>, 
